        "new_rules_in_this_unit": [
            "Form the Plusquamperfekt with hatte/war (Präteritum of haben/sein) + past participle to express events that happened before the main narrative.",
            "Use nachdem as a subordinating conjunction (verb to end); the nachdem-clause uses a tense one step earlier than the main clause."
